text: Jeff Fischer (born 1968) is an American voice actor. He is known for his work in commercials, cartoons, and video games. In 2005 he was chosen to announce the Teen Choice Awards. He is mostly known for his role as Jeff Fischer in American Dad!. ==Other websites== *Jeff Fischer at the Internet Movie Database.
